videos.description: Quarterback Ryan Finley keeps the ball and gets a push into the end zone from the 3-yard line. The Wolfpack would miss the extra point.
videos.headline: NC State strikes first with Finley TD

videos.description: Nathan Elliott looks down field and finds Anthony Ratliff-Williams for a long touchdown to give UNC the lead in the first quarter.
videos.headline: UNC's Ratliff-Williams hauls in 51-yard TD pass

videos.description: Michael Carter jumps up to catch Nathan Elliot's 24-yard pass to add to UNC's lead.
videos.headline: Elliot connects with Carter for Tar Heel TD

videos.description: Nathan Elliot is sacked by Darian Roseboro for a loss of 16 yards to help stall the Tar Heels' drive.
videos.headline: NC State's defense gets big sack to stop UNC

videos.description: Ryan Finley keeps the ball and runs it in from the 5-yard line cutting UNC's lead in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Finley scores again for the Wolfpack

videos.description: Ryan Finley scrambles and then his pass is picked off by Myles Wolfolk to give UNC possession as the first half ends.
videos.headline: NC State's Finley throws interception before halftime

videos.description: Nyheim Hines breaks for a 54-yard run to the end zone to give NC State the lead in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Wolfpack takes lead with big TD run

videos.description: Nathan Elliott's pass is tipped and then Airius Moore dives to make the catch for the interception to continue the momentum in NC State's favor.
videos.headline: Moore makes amazing diving catch for INT

videos.description: Nyheim Hines breaks for another big touchdown run to make it a two possession game in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: NC State capitalizes with 48-yard TD run

videos.description: Nathan Elliott connects with Jordan Cunningham for a 1-yard score to make it a one possession game.
videos.headline: UNC answers with short passing TD

videos.description: Germaine Pratt picks off Nathan Elliott's pass and returns it 73-yards to seal the Wolfpack's win over the Tar Heels.
videos.headline: NC State seals with win interception
